    <section id="id4753753">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id14606022"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis> The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id5015340"><emphasis effect="bold">Assessment Standard 1.12:</emphasis> We know this when the learner recognises, describes and uses:</para>
      <para id="id6929442"><emphasis effect="bold">1.12.1:</emphasis> divisibility rules for 2, 5, 10, 100 and 1 000.</para>
    </section>
